title: The Great Collection of Ska Music
description:
The Great Collection of Ska Music

This is a collection of ska diveded into 3 categories. First the original ska musik from the 60&#039;s. Then the ska revival era from the 80&#039;s and finelly the third wave ska revival and ska punk manily from the 90&#039;s.


The songs are of diffrent quality. Some from the 60&#039;s are rather poor mostley due to the recordings, so no complaints about poor quality.
